Thumani Mabwe murume akaberekwa mugore ra 1972 mudunhu raShe Makoni kuRusape. Akadzidza pachikoro chikuru che[[University of Zimbabwe]] apo akaverenga BSc Engineering. Murume uyu anonyora zvinyorwa aine chinagwa chokuti isu vatema tinge tichiumba mitauro yedu. Chishuvo chake kuti tigone kutaura zviri muzvidzidzo zve: Science, Mathematics, Law, Commerce tichishandisa rurimi rwedu. 

 

Parizvino akanyora zvinyorwa zvinoti: [[Kupimanzvimbo]]; [[Nhevedzwa dzeMvura]]; [[Mwaka yepaNyika]]; [[Hushangazhi]]; [[Nyeredzi]]; [[Fundoyetsimba]]; [[Gumbapamwe reMushana]], nezvimwewo zviri mu[[bumbiro]] reWikipedia yeShona. 


Iye anoti rwendo rungataridzika serwakareba asika, rwendo runotanga nenhanho imwe. Anoda kukurudzira vatema kuti, "tidade nerudzi rwedu, chimiro chedu nedzinza redu" - kuriko kuimba kwakaita muimbi, [[Oliver Mtukudzi]].
